You see a man-sized, convoluted mass of pinkish fungal matter. It really does look like a giant brain... two "eyes" the size of dinner plates stare unblinkingly at you from deep folds in the brain's surface. The entire mass is supported by four bony limbs which appear to be the remains of human arms and legs.
*DESCRIPTION_END
