NAME Padraig
*DESCRIPTION_START
You see Padraig Mcfoony, a grumpy old codger who doesn't know he's dead yet. He has a long white beard and dull blue eyes. He can't see you too well with them either. The most unusual thing however, is the meat cleaver sticking out of his head -- poor old guy still doesn't know what hit him.
